  "instructions": [
    "Wash and halve the baby plum tomatoes; set aside.",
    "In a large bowl, combine arugula, watercress, spinach, and sliced red onion.",
    "Add the halved tomatoes and capers to the greens; toss gently.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together olive oil, Dijon mustard, apple cider vinegar, salt, pepper, and parsley to make the dressing.",
    "Pour the dressing over the salad and toss until evenly coated.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning if needed.",
    "Serve immediately or chill for 10 minutes for extra crispness."
